uss.com.hk/t/ab7125/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250708/20250708_935aca9f833e9423d29aOw8XV98qkwC2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16353665_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16353665&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250708_164709_Facebook.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (250.29 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-8 16:48&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31976792&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1711870834686cef4a4fb555_07179357"/><published>2025-07-08T16:48:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>e1c45d18bfef6ce587934cab47866537</id><title>繼英皇國際後 再有發展商響警報 佳明宣布違貸款財務契諾</title><updated>2025-07-08T17:02:07+08:00</updated><author><name>柯爛屎</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-08T17:02:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573151765"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573151765"&gt;本港中小型發展商財務狀況，持續受到市場人士關注，繼英皇國際（0163）截至3月底共有166.05億元的銀行借貸已逾期或違反若干條款，銀行有可能要求立即償還有關借貸（即俗稱「Call Loan」）後，佳明集團（1271）指出，根據截至今年3月31日止之年度業績，未能履行與貸款方訂立之貸款融資項下有關的財務契諾，貸款方有權宣布公司須即時支付有關貸款本金額、應計利息及其他應付款項。&lt;br&gt;公司又指出，目前尚未償還之貸款本金總額約為47.95億元，就違反事項已取得若干貸款方的豁免為27.47億元。&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 繼英皇國際後再有發展商響警報佳明宣布違貸款財務契諾 | 香港01 https://www.hk01.com/article/60254547?utm_source=01articlecopy&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31976801&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1711870834686cef4a4fb555_07179357"/><published>2025-07-08T17:02:07+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d3b05d8e38fa079f04ccf702a8b1990d</id><title>大陸電視機市佔率最高，都發盈驚，真定假？</title><updated>2025-07-08T17:11:23+08:00</updated><author><name>eighth</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-08T17:11:23+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573151861"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573151861"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16353734" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573151861" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250708/20250708_2eb8fadf654f5f0b1486JbUXES5CIuls.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c22e83/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250708/20250708_2eb8fadf654f5f0b1486JbUXES5CIuls.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16353734_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16353734&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250708_170918_Bing.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (524.8 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-8 17:11&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31976808&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1711870834686cef4a4fb555_07179357"/><published>2025-07-08T17:11:23+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>8a220d540a5cb4e0f77e4c1438507ef9</id><title>一天分兩次買入/沽出同一只港股，要支付兩次佣金費用？</title><updated>2025-07-08T17:14:25+08:00</updated><author><name>4仔大朗</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-08T17:14:25+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573151877"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573151877"&gt;在香港買賣股票的交易費用包括經紀佣金及政府相關交易徵費。如果客戶一天內分二次或多次以相同或不同價格買入/沽出同一只股票，所有交易收費最終是根據客戶買入/沽出股票的總成交金額來計算的。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;如以總成交金額計算，所得出的佣金額少于港幣100元(不論客戶佣金率是多少)，我司亦會收取港幣100元作為最低佣金。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31976810&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1711870834686cef4a4fb555_07179357"/><published>2025-07-08T17:14:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ee25acd199e2a095696bb14d7c700082</id><title>三個見頂訊號，若同時出現，應開始沽貨離場！</title><updated>2025-07-08T17:30:36+08:00</updated><author><name>stephenie.sun</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-08T17:30:36+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573152056"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573152056"&gt;388 港交所市值突破一萬億人民幣&lt;br&gt;700 騰訊股價突破一千元人民幣&lt;br/&gt;939 建行股價升穿1倍市賬率&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31976819&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1711870834686cef4a4fb555_07179357"/><published>2025-07-08T17:30:36+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>536630f73085bc575fb1955fcb827a72</id><title>2025夏 快閃清州~全新航點</title><updated>2025-07-01T06:04:24+08:00</updated><author><name>stevenchoi</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-01T06:04:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573057096